Inferno's gun landed with a clank against the bases wall then he was 
slammed into the ground leaving a dent against his armor. Inferno 
quickly drew his other gun and fired an energy blast at the bot

--- In nbwrpg@y..., "warriorazure" <wingedwarrior41@h...> wrote:
> The gunfire hitting the ground under which the wormbot stood 
revealed 
> him. He immediately transformed back to robot mode andhopped out of 
> his hole. He fired at Inferno's gun as precisely as he could and 
threw 
> his tentacules at the antbot's legs, trying to smash him hard to 
the 
> ground. His eyes were full of fury as he saw that already, SS was 
> down, but Warhead was in an even worse condition.
> 
> The predacon warrior was lying on his back. Four holes passing 
through 
> him marked where the lasers had burned their way. His agony was 
still 
> lasting, though, and the pain he endured was tremendous. His 
strength 
> effectively vanished, making all attempts to make a sound utterly 
> useless. He still lived, but his spark would not stay for long...
